com.sun.star.uno
Interface IMethodDescription

All Superinterfaces:
IMemberDescription
public interface IMethodDescription
extends IMemberDescription

The IMethodDescription allows to examine a method in detail. It gives a view to java methods from a UNO point.

Since:
UDK3.0
